1. Licenses in this project 

a) Source code
The source code of this project, usually located in the "src" directory, is published under the MIT license. For the text of the license, please refer to section 3.

b) Technical information
All technical information in this project is published under the Creative Commons Attibution-NonCommercial 4.0 international license. 

The term "technical information" thereby refers to all hardware and drawing thereof in this project, including but not limited to the clocks frame, housing, front panel, electronic control board and alike. All technical information is commonly stored in the "cad" and "pcb" directories. 

For the text of the license, please refer to section 3.

2. Dependencies

The source code in this project relies on a set of libraries, that can be downloaded and installed independently from the Arduino library manager. These dependencies are licensed under varying licenses. 
Dependencies are not included in this project. It is left to the attention of the user to acquire a licensed copy of each of the dependencies independent of this project.

The list below lists the dependencies and their according license.

Adafuit | Neopixel | GNU LGPL | https://github.com/adafruit/Adafruit_NeoPixel
NorthernWidget | DS3231 | The unlicense | https://github.com/NorthernWidget/DS3231
NicoHood | PinChangeInterrupt | MIT license | https://github.com/NicoHood/PinChangeInterrupt


